name: GebProxyIncentivesActions
description: Incentives proxy actions. These functions are meant to be used as a a library for a DSProxy. Some are unsafe if you call them directly. This contract is supposed to be used alongside a DSProxy contract.

functionDecorators.name: allowHandler
functionDecorators.description: Allow/disallow a usr address to quit to the sender handler.

parameterDecorators.name: usr
parameterDecorators.description: address - usr address uint ok - 1 for allowed.

functionDecorators.name: allowSAFE
functionDecorators.description: Allow/disallow a usr address to manage the safe.

parameterDecorators.name: usr
parameterDecorators.description: address - usr address uint ok - 1 for allowed.

functionDecorators.name: approveSAFEModification
functionDecorators.description: Approves an address to modify the Safe.

parameterDecorators.name: usr
parameterDecorators.description: address - Address allowed to modify Safe.

functionDecorators.name: denySAFEModification
functionDecorators.description: Denies an address to modify the Safe.

parameterDecorators.name: usr
parameterDecorators.description: address - Address disallowed to modify Safe.

functionDecorators.name: enterSystem
functionDecorators.description: Import a position from src handler to the handler owned by safe.

functionDecorators.name: ethJoin_join
functionDecorators.description: Joins the system with the full msg.value.

functionDecorators.name: ethJoin_join
functionDecorators.description: Joins the system with the a specified value.

functionDecorators.name: exitAndRemoveLiquidity
functionDecorators.description: Exits from liquidity mining pool and removes liquidity from Uniswap.

parameterDecorators.name: minTokenAmounts
parameterDecorators.description: uint[2] - minimum ETH/Token amounts when providing liquidity to Uniswap (user set acceptable slippage).

functionDecorators.name: exitETH
functionDecorators.description: Exits ETH (wad) from balance available in the handler.

functionDecorators.name: exitMine
functionDecorators.description: Exits liquidity mining pool (withdraw LP tokens and getRewards for current campaign).

functionDecorators.name: exitRemoveLiquidityRepayDebt
functionDecorators.description: Exits from liquidity mining pool, removes liquidity from Uniswap and repays debt.

parameterDecorators.name: minTokenAmounts
parameterDecorators.description: uint[2] - minimum ETH/Token amounts when providing liquidity to Uniswap (user set acceptable slippage).

functionDecorators.name: freeETH
functionDecorators.description: Free ETH (wad) from safe and sends it to msg.sender.

functionDecorators.name: generateDebt
functionDecorators.description: Generates debt and sends COIN amount to msg.sender.

functionDecorators.name: generateDebtAndProvideLiquidityStake
functionDecorators.description: Generates debt and sends COIN amount (deltaWad) and provides it as liquidity to Uniswap and stakes LP tokens in Farm.

parameterDecorators.name: minTokenAmounts
parameterDecorators.description: uint[2] - minimum ETH/Token amounts when providing liquidity to Uniswap (user set acceptable slippage).

functionDecorators.name: generateDebtAndProvideLiquidityUniswap
functionDecorators.description: Generates debt and sends COIN amount (deltaWad) and provides it as liquidity to Uniswap.

parameterDecorators.name: wad
parameterDecorators.description: uint - Amount of debt to generate.

parameterDecorators.name: minTokenAmounts
parameterDecorators.description: uint[2] - minimum ETH/Token amounts when providing liquidity to Uniswap (user set acceptable slippage).

functionDecorators.name: getRewards
functionDecorators.description: Harvests rewards available (both instant and staked).

functionDecorators.name: getWethPair
functionDecorators.description: Returns the address of a token-weth pair.

functionDecorators.name: lockETH
functionDecorators.description: Lock ETH (msg.value) as collateral in safe.

functionDecorators.name: lockETHAndGenerateDebt
functionDecorators.description: Locks Eth, generates debt and sends COIN amount (deltaWad) to msg.sender.

functionDecorators.name: lockETHGenerateDebtProvideLiquidityStake
functionDecorators.description: Locks Eth, generates debt and sends COIN amount (deltaWad) and provides it as liquidity to Uniswap and stakes LP tokens in Farm.

parameterDecorators.name: deltaWad
parameterDecorators.description: uint - Amount of debt to generate.

parameterDecorators.name: liquidityWad
parameterDecorators.description: uint - Amount of ETH to be provided as liquidity (the remainder of msg.value will be used to collateralize the Safe).

parameterDecorators.name: minTokenAmounts
parameterDecorators.description: uint[2] - minimum ETH/Token amounts when providing liquidity to Uniswap (user set acceptable slippage).

functionDecorators.name: lockETHGenerateDebtProvideLiquidityUniswap
functionDecorators.description: Locks Eth, generates debt and sends COIN amount (deltaWad) and provides it as liquidity to Uniswap.

parameterDecorators.name: deltaWad
parameterDecorators.description: uint - Amount of debt to generate.

parameterDecorators.name: liquidityWad
parameterDecorators.description: uint - Amount of ETH to be provided as liquidity (the remainder of msg.value will be used to collateralize the Safe).

parameterDecorators.name: minTokenAmounts
parameterDecorators.description: uint[2] - minimum ETH/Token amounts when providing liquidity to Uniswap (user set acceptable slippage).

functionDecorators.name: migrateCampaign
functionDecorators.description: Migrates from one campaign to another, claiming rewards.

functionDecorators.name: modifySAFECollateralization
functionDecorators.description: Modify a SAFE's collateralization ratio while keeping the generated COIN or collateral freed in the SAFE handler address.

functionDecorators.name: moveSAFE
functionDecorators.description: Move a position from safeSrc handler to the safeDst handler.

functionDecorators.name: openLockETHAndGenerateDebt
functionDecorators.description: Opens Safe, locks Eth, generates debt and sends COIN amount (deltaWad) to msg.sender.

functionDecorators.name: openLockETHGenerateDebtProvideLiquidityStake
functionDecorators.description: Opens Safe, locks Eth, generates debt and sends COIN amount (deltaWad) and provides it as liquidity to Uniswap and stakes LP tokens in Farm.

parameterDecorators.name: collateralType
parameterDecorators.description: bytes32 - The ETH type used to generate debt.

parameterDecorators.name: deltaWad
parameterDecorators.description: uint256 - Amount of debt to generate.

parameterDecorators.name: liquidityWad
parameterDecorators.description: uint256 - Amount of ETH to be provided as liquidity (the remainder of msg.value will be used to collateralize the Safe).

parameterDecorators.name: minTokenAmounts
parameterDecorators.description: uint[2] - minimum ETH/Token amounts when providing liquidity to Uniswap (user set acceptable slippage).

functionDecorators.name: openLockETHGenerateDebtProvideLiquidityUniswap
functionDecorators.description: Opens Safe, locks Eth, generates debt and sends COIN amount (deltaWad) and provides it as liquidity to Uniswap.

parameterDecorators.name: collateralType
parameterDecorators.description: bytes32 - The ETH type used to generate debt.

parameterDecorators.name: deltaWad
parameterDecorators.description: uint - Amount of debt to generate.

parameterDecorators.name: liquidityWad
parameterDecorators.description: uint - Amount of ETH to be provided as liquidity (the remainder of msg.value will be used to collateralize the Safe).

parameterDecorators.name: minTokenAmounts
parameterDecorators.description: uint[2] - minimum ETH/Token amounts when providing liquidity to Uniswap (user set acceptable slippage).

functionDecorators.name: openSAFE
functionDecorators.description: Opens a brand new Safe.

functionDecorators.name: provideLiquidityStake
functionDecorators.description: Generates debt and sends COIN amount (deltaWad) and provides it as liquidity to Uniswap and stakes LP tokens in Farm.

parameterDecorators.name: minTokenAmounts
parameterDecorators.description: uint[2] - minimum ETH/Token amounts when providing liquidity to Uniswap (user set acceptable slippage).

functionDecorators.name: provideLiquidityUniswap
functionDecorators.description: Provides liquidity to Uniswap.

parameterDecorators.name: wad
parameterDecorators.description: uint - Amount of coin to provide (msg.value for ETH).

parameterDecorators.name: minTokenAmounts
parameterDecorators.description: uint[2] - minimum ETH/Token amounts when providing liquidity to Uniswap (user set acceptable slippage).

functionDecorators.name: quitSystem
functionDecorators.description: Quit the system, migrating the safe (lockedCollateral, generatedDebt) to a different dst handler.

functionDecorators.name: removeLiquidityUniswap
functionDecorators.description: Removes liquidity from Uniswap.

parameterDecorators.name: value
parameterDecorators.description: uint - Amount of LP tokens to remove.

parameterDecorators.name: minTokenAmounts
parameterDecorators.description: uint[2] - minimum ETH/Token amounts when providing liquidity to Uniswap (user set acceptable slippage).

functionDecorators.name: repayDebt
functionDecorators.description: Repays debt.

functionDecorators.name: repayDebtAndFreeETH
functionDecorators.description: Repays debt and frees ETH (sends it to msg.sender).

parameterDecorators.name: collateralWad
parameterDecorators.description: uint - Amount of collateral to free.

parameterDecorators.name: deltaWad
parameterDecorators.description: uint - Amount of debt to repay.

functionDecorators.name: stakeInMine
functionDecorators.description: Stakes in liquidity mining pool.

functionDecorators.name: transfer
functionDecorators.description: ERC20 transfer.

functionDecorators.name: transferCollateral
functionDecorators.description: Transfer wad amount of safe collateral from the safe address to a dst address.

parameterDecorators.name: dst
parameterDecorators.description: address - destination address uint wad - amount.

functionDecorators.name: transferInternalCoins
functionDecorators.description: Transfer rad amount of COIN from the safe address to a dst address.

parameterDecorators.name: dst
parameterDecorators.description: address - destination address uint rad - amount.

functionDecorators.name: transferSAFEOwnership
functionDecorators.description: Transfer the ownership of a proxy owned Safe.

functionDecorators.name: transferSAFEOwnershipToProxy
functionDecorators.description: Transfer the ownership to a new proxy owned by a different address.

parameterDecorators.name: dst
parameterDecorators.description: address - Owner of the new proxy.

functionDecorators.name: withdrawAndHarvest
functionDecorators.description: Withdraw LP tokens from liquidity mining pool and harvests rewards.

functionDecorators.name: withdrawAndRemoveLiquidity
functionDecorators.description: Withdraws from liquidity mining pool and removes liquidity from Uniswap.

parameterDecorators.name: minTokenAmounts
parameterDecorators.description: uint[2] - minimum ETH/Token amounts when providing liquidity to Uniswap (user set acceptable slippage).

functionDecorators.name: withdrawFromMine
functionDecorators.description: Withdraw LP tokens from liquidity mining pool.

functionDecorators.name: withdrawHarvestRemoveLiquidity
functionDecorators.description: Withdraw LP tokens from liquidity mining pool and harvests rewards.

parameterDecorators.name: minTokenAmounts
parameterDecorators.description: uint[2] - minimum ETH/Token amounts when providing liquidity to Uniswap (user set acceptable slippage).

functionDecorators.name: withdrawRemoveLiquidityRepayDebt
functionDecorators.description: Withdraws from liquidity mining pool, removes liquidity from Uniswap and repays debt.

parameterDecorators.name: minTokenAmounts
parameterDecorators.description: uint[2] - minimum ETH/Token amounts when providing liquidity to Uniswap (user set acceptable slippage).
